Class RealTimeEmergencyMenu

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.cst.view.RealTimeEmergencyMenu
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    DistanceTravelledListener, EmergencyCallDispatchListener, OperationFinishedListener, OperationStartedListener, TripStartedListener

    public class RealTimeEmergencyMenu
extends Object
implements EmergencyCallDispatchListener, TripStartedListener, DistanceTravelledListener, OperationStartedListener, OperationFinishedListener
    RealTimeEmergencyMeu class Ties up all systems together and launches the emergency system. Handles all console ouput for every event.
